# Cognitive OS - Environment Variables
# This repository is a specification repo and requires no external services.
# No environment variables are needed to develop or contribute.
#
# If integrating Cognitive OS into a project that uses GitNexus or merge CLI,
# the following may be relevant (but are NOT required for this repo):
#
# GITNEXUS_API_URL=        # GitNexus impact analysis endpoint
# MERGE_CLI_KEY=           # merge CLI authentication key
